{{Quote|The last Human who tried to fly one of our ships crashed into the N'rakti Lava Fields. Your pilots would fall out of the sky like damp moths.|[[Poggle the Lesser/Legends|Poggle the Lesser]]|<ref name="The New Essential Guide to Vehicles and Vessels">''[[The New Essential Guide to Vehicles and Vessels]]''</ref>}}
The '''N'rakti Lava Fields''' were a [[Volcano/Legends|volcanic]] region on [[Geonosis/Legends|Geonosis]]. A [[Human/Legends|Human]] trying to fly a [[Nantex-class territorial defense starfighter|Geonosian starfighter]] crashed in the fields.

